France: Imported Case of Dengue virus Type 1
--------------------------------------------
On 15 Jun 2002, we isolated in Marseilles dengue virus type 1 from the
blood of a traveller who had returned from French Polynesia after a [stay]
of one month in Moorea Island.
--
Dr Guillaume Durand
Diagnosis of arbovirus - IMTSSA
Parc du Pharo
13998 - Marseille armees
